Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:05.53,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:09.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Dad and Mom were fighting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:25.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:33.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the pet I used to own as a child…\N{\i1}Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:38.90,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, could you wash properly behind my ears too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:40.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's because you're moving too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:42.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't splash so much… Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:44.21,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,More towards the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:44.91,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh… where?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:46.31,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:50.55,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, that feels good~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:55.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this is the pet "Momo" I now own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:01:01.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was on a rainy day two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:03.60,signs,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Two weeks ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.09,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Let me see…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:07.73,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,the last time I cried was when I was in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:11.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It was when my pet died after getting sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:13.14,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Since then, I've never cried again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:15.54,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, and when I broke a bone during Aikidou,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:18.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I felt the tears coming, but I didn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.98,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Lately I don't even laugh much because I've been too busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:25.35,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,That's not very healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:30.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,My coworkers call me names like cyborg,\NNoh-men and kokeshi doll behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:32.79,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,But you're so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:33.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.45,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I got dumped by a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:37.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He said that I lacked a sense of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:40.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He says he feels inferior when he's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:45.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Well, I graduated from Tokyo University and have experience studying abroad at Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:48.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He was lower than me in income, educational background, even in height.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But the one who cheated was not I, but him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:56.01,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sick of men and their inferiority complexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not that I still feel any attachment, nor am I hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:00.45,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:05.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,My head has been hurting for ten days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:08.06,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.63,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:13.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,This is my first time coming to a place like this so I don't know much,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:16.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,but do you prescribe medication? Like a tranquilizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:17.93,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Well, let's try to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:19.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.34,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Let me see you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:33.38,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I see… it is true. You do lack a sense of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:38.79,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Today's people are dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:44.33,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,And a smile is like a drop of water falling onto their dry hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.40,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,A beautiful drop of water… don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:50.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No. I don't quite understand what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.33,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,No matter how beautiful and successful you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:57.37,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,if you are not able to offer that water to people, as a person, you are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The worst?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.81,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Even a kokeshi doll could be considered cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.15,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, that'll be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:08.37,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Forgive me, I have not yet made my diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.05,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:13.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was the stupid one for coming to counseling just for a slight headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.06,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Did you love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:20.00,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,That man who was lower than you in height and income.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:26.07,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I have just the cure for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.34,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Try crying…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:31.87,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:37.88,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, I'd rather die than cry in front of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.89,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Next patient, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:02.80,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,You're lucky… you're pretty and smart…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:16.69,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Honestly speaking, it's easier for me to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Kuraki-san, where are the papers that I asked for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.40,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'll prepare them right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.90,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you start preparing them now, how much time will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:10.60,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Oh, umm… about an hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you absolutely by 2 o'clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.98,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Nevermind… I'll prepare them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.40,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:21.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's all right.\NIt's my fault for asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.36,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,I see Iwaya-san is scary as usual…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.29,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,It's okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:38.93,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,I know I'm not as smart as Iwaya-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.07,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.31,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Don't cry, you poor thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:47.64,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:49.78,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.25,petto,boss1,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san… don't cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.96,petto,boss1,0,0,0,,Don't behave like that when the government officials visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:00.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,My behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I just greeted them as I normally would.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.76,petto,boss1,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:08.53,petto,boss1,0,0,0,,Just because they touched your back a little, you don't have to get out of your seat like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:12.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but they didn't touch my back, they touched my rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.44,petto,boss1,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:20.38,petto,boss1,0,0,0,,Only Official Suzuki would have the guts to touch the butt of a fearsome woman like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:23.35,petto,boss1,0,0,0,,Normal men would be too scared to do that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.38,petto,boss1,0,0,0,,Don't look so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:31.15,petto,boss1,0,0,0,,Would you like me to touch it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shoot…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:57.01,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not like me to be angered by something trivial like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.56,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll either be a salary reduction or expulsion for improper behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:20.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.13,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is he dead…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What should I do… go to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.34,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, ambulance…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:18.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh… excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm… excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, good evening…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.28,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,What is this? This box?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.21,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh… this actually isn't my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.75,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,I told you[,] trash in bulk must be reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, this is different… I just found and picked it up just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.35,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Picked up? So it's an animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.52,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,I told you pets are not allowed in this appartment complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.72,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Let me look inside. Is it a doggy or a kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.02,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:29.16,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,It's even more suspicious that you try to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.87,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,I will have to inspect that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:33.50,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:33.99,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:34.47,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.30,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I guess first off, I should notify the police…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He's like a dog…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:13.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wow… 39 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.27,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It tastes good…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:38.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next morning, as the rain cleared,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:44.06,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}the headache that had lasted ten days had also disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.67,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh… oh man, the report!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:38.51,title,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Kimi wa petto\NYou are my pet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.51,episode,text,0,0,0,,[sign]1. How to care for a beautiful boy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:49.02,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Shibusawa Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.73,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,You know Goda Takeshi, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:57.97,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Of course you know him…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.10,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,he's your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.21,petto,girl,0,0,0,,What's this old man talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:04.12,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,I want to know his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:13.42,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,If I knew, I would go see him myself, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:18.92,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Leave her alone, Rumi and Takeshi just broke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:22.86,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Don't say insensitive things to her, you old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.36,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:32.23,petto,girl,0,0,0,,this man just asked us for prostitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:43.88,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Stupid Takeshi…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please eat the soft rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:58.73,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have no appetite, I think you should eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:02.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will take the key with me, so you can go home whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:31.09,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,What? You let a boy sleep at your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.63,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's just how things ended up in the course of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:36.63,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Sumire, even someone like you has to be careful about that kind of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean, a person like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.00,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'm just saying, even with a strong person like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.91,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,it could be dangerous to let a young man into the house so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:50.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He has a delicate build. Plus, his arm was injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.68,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Injured? That seems even more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.90,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,He could be involved with something dangerous, like the yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's hard to believe…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,As soon as he wakes up, I'm sure he'll just obediently go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:02.69,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You make it sound like he's a stray cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:05.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it, Yuri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.29,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:10.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He reminds me of Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:10.80,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:14.74,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Wasn't Momo the dog you used to own back in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah. So I felt like I couldn't just leave him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.48,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.18,petto,boss1,0,0,0,,Iwaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:27.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, chief. I'm really sorry about yester—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.70,announcement,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Official announcement:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:41.90,announcement2,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Iwaya Sumire of the External Affairs department will be transferred to the Lifestyle department.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:42.33,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Look, Iwaya-san from External Affairs is being moved to Lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.17,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,What? From External Affairs to Lifestyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.00,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,That sucks, she was such an elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:48.20,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,I heard she punched out the External Affairs chief and knocked out his front tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.50,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:56.47,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Yeah, and she just got called to the Head Chief's office…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:59.15,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.18,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Long time, no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:39.19,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.56,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Here is your ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:44.73,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.23,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:58.67,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,This is your spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You could've just thrown it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:05.95,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Sorry, were you busy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:09.65,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not particularly. How is your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:11.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Her baby's due next month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.76,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:24.57,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Huh? Uhh… I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:27.94,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,how are you lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:32.31,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Does it look like I've been spending my days crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:44.45,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,But… you got transferred to the Lifestyle department, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:48.42,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I heard you had some trouble with your department chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.26,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,so I was kind of worried…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:54.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He just broke his front tooth. In any case, it has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.97,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,You don't have to talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.74,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,It's pretty hard on you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:11.35,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Because I know that deep down, you're a very timid and thoughtful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:18.79,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I can't support you in a time like this, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:23.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Just because we went out for a mere two and a half years, don't act like you know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.03,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:27.63,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.53,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But don't expect any gift from me when your baby's born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:30.53,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Your check?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:32.03,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,There's nothing a woman can gain from being strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:35.90,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sometimes I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.88,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.82,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,That was Iwaya-san's ex-boyfriend that just came, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:56.06,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Oh, that guy from the Printing department.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:59.36,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,I guess they broke up after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.86,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Well, I saw it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.33,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Who would really feel comfortable with a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.43,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,higher than you in educational background, salary, and even height?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.44,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Shh!! She'll hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:04.56,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.80,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't have any money to ride the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:17.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It was de~licious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really? I'm happy to see you're feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:25.15,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks to you, I'm feeling great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:26.65,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then please go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:29.88,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Or perhaps I should notify the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:40.70,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.30,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I just drank some water a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:44.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's fine, it's just water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:49.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But I was lucky to be found by a good person like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.07,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,When I catch a cold before spring, it ends up becoming asthma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:54.31,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Found? Are you some kind of stray dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:57.01,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah, close. I don't have a place to live right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:59.50,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Lately, I've been staying here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:02.85,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Last night a hotel owner suddenly attacked me—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:03.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Attacked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:04.29,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:06.35,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I thought I was lucky he was letting me stay for free,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:07.86,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,but then he told me to pay him back with my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:09.76,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But I couldn't bring myself to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:12.83,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,so I ran away as fast as I could, but the guys who were chasing me were so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:15.40,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I was hiding in that box, and before I knew it, I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:17.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:22.77,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Until now, I've met all kinds of nice people,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:28.98,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,but this is the first time I've met someone as kind as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:34.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I helped you yesterday because I felt I had to,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:36.62,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,but I normally don't let strange men into my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:39.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you're that healthy, get out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:40.92,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll give you money for the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:43.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.56,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Just a moment ago, you told me you were feeling great! Where's your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:47.00,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I want to eat some curry—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:48.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you to decide the dinner menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:50.53,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm asking you where you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:52.70,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:54.77,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.44,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I want to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:01.78,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Please! Can you let me stay here for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:05.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ouch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:07.42,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:08.02,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I won't ask you to make me your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.02,0:23:08.95,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:11.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,None of your business! I'm not interested in younger men anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:12.22,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:14.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Whether I like younger men or not isn't your business either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:18.83,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Lady, you're an interesting person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:21.53,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You're good at cooking, and I think we'd get along great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:25.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ha! I'm a cold hard-core career woman. Not an interesting person at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:30.07,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,This morning, when I woke up, I felt sooo happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:32.73,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,There was food, and blankets, and your sweet smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:33.55,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't smell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:35.34,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I felt that I wanted to stay here together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:37.55,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you keep talking nonsense, I'll call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:24:01.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Phew… If that gossipy landlord saw such a scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,who knows what he would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:05.84,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.28,0:24:12.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's no use looking at me with those puppy dog eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.98,0:24:14.95,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Then anything, I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:16.38,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'll play your younger brother, or I can be your playmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:18.99,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'll be your bodyguard, or a gangster, or even a masseur.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:20.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.30,0:24:21.49,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.00,0:24:25.09,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't you have any kind of pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.33,0:24:26.43,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.20,0:24:28.90,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in K-1 anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.20,0:24:28.90,announcement2,text,0,0,0,,[note]K-1 is professional wrestling championship
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.90,0:24:31.80,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I dunno, something about professional wrestling… the muscles…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.83,0:24:34.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then why don't you become my pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.14,0:24:38.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I could let you stay here as a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.67,0:24:40.51,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.74,0:24:41.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:45.65,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you're good, I'll take care of you and cook for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.75,0:24:49.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But you won't have any rights, and you'll have to obey everything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.75,0:24:51.55,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.59,0:24:53.70,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't get any rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.80,0:24:55.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, because you'd be a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.29,0:24:57.33,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.33,0:24:58.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes. You can't comply, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.46,0:24:59.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then please leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.23,0:25:06.00,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Ruff!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.60,0:25:07.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wan?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.44,0:25:11.97,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll become your pet. Man, that's it? How lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.97,0:25:14.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait, do you know what this means? By pet…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.15,0:25:18.95,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.69,0:25:33.19,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Making a boy a pet is not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.19,0:25:35.53,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,This is good. It's really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.70,0:25:37.73,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not human, it's not common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.07,0:25:41.04,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.04,0:25:43.30,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,a person who talks a lot to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.71,0:25:45.41,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,There's a lot of housewives like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.41,0:25:48.38,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,who mumble to themselves about their husbands' coming home late, and single women…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.41,0:25:50.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to ask you one more time—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.11,0:25:51.35,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'll become your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.85,0:25:57.29,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,By the way, you've asked that question for the 14th time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.29,0:26:00.46,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You can't take it back now and say you won't take care of me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.46,0:26:02.86,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't want to be sent off to the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.73,0:26:08.50,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food! I'm grateful again to my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.50,0:26:10.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't have any intention of sleeping with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.13,0:26:13.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you surprised about? Of course I wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.17,0:26:16.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Just because I let you live here with me, I don't want you to get such loose ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.51,0:26:20.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wanted to be by myself for a while anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.28,0:26:23.45,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I didn't feel like living with a man for a while, and now I'm not even interested in men.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.65,0:26:27.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sick of their selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.32,0:26:30.52,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I feel inferior…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.65,0:26:33.19,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,when I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.36,0:26:36.02,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Just because they're not as successful as a woman they feel tormented.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.89,0:26:38.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Seems so stupid…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.36,0:26:40.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,he is stupid and I'm stupid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.03,0:26:42.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Even though I graduated from Tokyo University, I went out with that kink of a guy for two and a half years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.70,0:26:46.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh well, enough about that. What I'm trying to say is…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.38,0:26:54.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.51,0:26:56.58,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.08,0:27:00.05,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I felt full and before I knew it…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.05,0:27:02.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you a really weird person?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.88,0:27:07.56,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, come to think of it, my friends often tell me, "You're really weird."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.12,0:27:10.39,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,My girlfriend always called me "stupid".
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.19,0:27:12.86,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Well, I already broke up with her though.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.06,0:27:15.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's good, I think it was right to break up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.50,0:27:19.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But as a pet, I think I'd do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.03,0:27:20.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Listen to what a person is saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.17,0:27:26.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.40,0:27:28.41,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,The pose of submission.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.41,0:27:31.18,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I submit to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.18,0:27:34.78,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,If you say no sex, then I won't do anything inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.95,0:27:38.39,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,If you say you want me to, then I can do that for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.39,0:27:39.19,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.19,0:27:41.79,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,And your pet can even do acts like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.13,0:27:53.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.40,0:27:54.24,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.20,0:27:57.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah, I kind of feel like rewarding you with food.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.84,0:27:58.67,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.81,0:28:02.74,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I won't disobey you, and I will do anything to make my master happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.74,0:28:05.55,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,And I wouldn't do anything to hurt you, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.32,0:28:09.92,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is your arm okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.62,0:28:13.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yup, thanks to my master's care.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.86,0:28:15.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh and, just to let you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.82,0:28:19.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I love them — K-1, pride, and professional wrestling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.96,0:28:23.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you're serious about living here, don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.77,0:28:31.74,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.48,0:28:36.04,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.04,0:28:38.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's all empty so you can use it freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.85,0:28:42.18,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.18,0:28:45.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,After 12, use the bath quietly,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.59,0:28:47.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,because the landlord will get annoyed if he gets complaints from the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.92,0:28:51.23,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh hey, can I have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.36,0:28:53.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can have it. I bought it and never used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.13,0:28:57.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,This is my bedroom, so make sure you don't enter it. And over there is the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.03,0:28:58.90,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Be absolutely sure to use it cleanly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.83,0:29:03.24,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, why is this apartment so big when you only live by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.84,0:29:07.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because I bought it with plans of getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.04,0:29:08.44,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What? You're getting married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.44,0:29:09.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.88,0:29:16.15,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The man got pregnant the girl he was cheating with and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.29,0:29:19.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.65,0:29:20.62,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.06,0:29:23.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's all right, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.12,0:29:25.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.13,0:29:28.83,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh man, forgot something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.83,0:29:29.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.36,0:29:31.20,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Your name. I haven't asked it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.20,0:29:32.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.20,0:29:35.30,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I know that, it's on your front door. I meant your first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.37,0:29:37.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Iwaya Sumire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.01,0:29:38.71,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.24,0:29:42.18,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I see, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.14,0:29:45.68,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-san,\NSumire-chan,\NSumire-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.68,0:29:46.55,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yo Sumire!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.55,0:29:47.38,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.55,0:29:47.78,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,SUMIRE!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.78,0:29:48.15,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.82,0:29:51.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Can you not repeat it like that? I don't like that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.39,0:29:53.46,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Then what do people call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.46,0:29:54.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,"Iwaya-san.'
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.29,0:29:56.62,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Even your ex?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.73,0:29:57.99,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, is there something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.99,0:30:00.00,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You don't have any nicknames?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.63,0:30:03.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.33,0:30:07.14,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Then I'll just call you Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.24,0:30:10.04,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You should let people call you that, it's such a pretty name.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.47,0:30:12.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.74,0:30:13.38,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.84,0:30:14.78,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.28,0:30:19.35,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Why don't you give me one? You can give me whatever name you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.35,0:30:21.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Because I'm your pet, that's how things work, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.72,0:30:23.89,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.89,0:30:26.59,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Anything is fine, your favorite celebrity's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.59,0:30:30.79,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,or the name of your first love, maybe the guy you lost your virginity to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.99,0:30:31.83,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.39,0:30:34.13,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Momo? Was he a foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.40,0:30:36.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's the name of the dog I used to own.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.20,0:30:37.47,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,A dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.47,0:30:39.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The way your hair curls looks just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.47,0:30:41.40,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Plus, that name is for a female dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.40,0:30:43.14,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You told me I could give you whatever name I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.21,0:30:53.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.08,0:30:54.18,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Just wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.42,0:31:03.22,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.19,0:31:07.06,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Here. You wouldn't want to use mine by accident, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.86,0:31:09.06,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.60,0:31:12.37,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.67,0:31:15.67,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,so I'm Momo from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.11,0:31:24.35,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.45,0:31:28.18,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Oh, Takeshi hasn't been coming recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.32,0:31:32.29,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,He was a kind of free wanderer in the first place so he doesn't really show up often.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.89,0:31:38.99,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Hey, are you part of the paparazzi? Or maybe a fan of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.99,0:31:40.80,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,There's a lot of them lately…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.80,0:31:41.90,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,male fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.90,0:31:43.90,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Uh, no, it's not really like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.40,0:31:49.07,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,But I don't think you have a chance…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.47,0:31:50.94,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,he's straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.14,0:31:53.07,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Although he's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.48,0:31:55.08,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.66,0:32:11.83,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Junpei?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.93,0:32:15.03,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just wondering what Takeshi's up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.03,0:32:17.50,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Huh? Did Takeshi contact you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.55,0:32:18.50,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.70,0:32:22.24,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Takeshi, Takeshi! Why is everyone so interested in him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.18,0:32:30.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I am Iwaya, recently transferred from the External Affairs department.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.51,0:32:31.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.98,0:32:34.85,petto,boss2,0,0,0,,Okay, gotcha. Your seat is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.29,0:32:41.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.81,0:32:59.54,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps this is…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.98,0:33:02.85,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}a very direct prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.92,0:33:06.10,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Yes… uhuh… I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.18,0:33:09.95,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Oh, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.82,0:33:16.02,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Yes, that would be very helpful actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.33,0:33:21.53,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.56,0:33:23.90,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh, Iwaya-san. How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.47,0:33:26.94,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,I am Ishida. I got moved to the Lifestyle department this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.94,0:33:28.27,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.27,0:33:29.27,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.80,0:33:32.67,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Umm, the one on the phone is Tsumeyama-san, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.67,0:33:35.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I know. After all, I work in the same company.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.24,0:33:38.25,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh yes, of course. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.25,0:33:42.22,petto,boss2,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey. Ishida recently came in, but here, he's an upper official.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.15,0:33:46.49,petto,boss2,0,0,0,,Don't have too much pride. That's why I don't like elite women.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.49,0:33:47.56,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Don't have to say—
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.56,0:33:48.89,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I apologize. Excuse my rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.89,0:33:52.13,petto,boss2,0,0,0,,Well if you've always walked the path of an elite,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.13,0:33:53.83,petto,boss2,0,0,0,,I suppose this place would be more of a demotion for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.83,0:33:54.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.03,0:33:58.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The Lifestyle column is the most widely read and covers the most genres.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.93,0:34:01.24,petto,boss2,0,0,0,,That kind of model answer gets on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.74,0:34:04.21,petto,boss2,0,0,0,,Oh, don't punch me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.21,0:34:06.71,petto,boss2,0,0,0,,I just fixed up these two front teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.94,0:34:12.21,petto,boss2,0,0,0,,It's worse that you're a woman who's intelligent and too strong for her own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.89,0:34:27.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.56,0:34:31.43,petto,girl,0,0,0,,What?! Iwaya-san's in the Lifestyle department now?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.43,0:34:33.40,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's kind of unlikely, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.40,0:34:35.37,petto,girl,0,0,0,,She's moved up her career at such a fast pace,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.37,0:34:37.71,petto,girl,0,0,0,,going from the branch and into the External Affairs department in just half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.71,0:34:40.78,petto,girl,0,0,0,,I heard she also broke up with Yoshida-san of the Printing department.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.04,0:34:42.78,petto,girl,0,0,0,,They didn't really go together in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.78,0:34:46.25,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Yeah, I mean, Iwaya-san was even taller than him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.82,0:34:48.68,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I don't know if I should say this, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.68,0:34:50.92,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,don't you feel like she kind of deserves it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.02,0:34:54.26,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,People who can do anything kind of get on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.26,0:34:55.72,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Like, "Who do you think you are?"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.72,0:34:57.83,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Oh, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.83,0:35:00.50,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Isn't that the reason Yoshida-san broke up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.00,0:35:03.00,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure that's part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.75,0:35:19.38,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.48,0:35:25.25,petto,man,0,0,0,,Hey, young lady, are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.72,0:35:27.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with being alone? I like being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.82,0:35:30.16,petto,man,0,0,0,,Don't say sad things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.86,0:35:36.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm not sad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.60,0:35:40.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Being alone is good. I like being alone. So leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.34,0:35:42.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.58,0:35:57.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.92,0:36:02.52,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.52,0:36:04.16,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wha— Stop…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.23,0:36:07.53,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan, I was waiting for you, all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.53,0:36:10.17,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I had so many things to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.17,0:36:13.00,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Just a little while ago on TV, they were showing these weird ghost pictures,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.00,0:36:15.64,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,and it was really stupid, but I couldn't stop laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.64,0:36:16.57,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.57,0:36:19.41,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,it looks like they're gonna show a wrestling match soon. They were showing a commercial for it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.41,0:36:21.88,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I think it starts at one o'clock? It's good that you got home in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.88,0:36:24.78,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh! And you know how there's a planting pot by your window?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.78,0:36:26.25,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Did you know there's a bud coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.25,0:36:29.78,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's purple, and really tiny, but what kind of flower is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.89,0:36:40.30,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.77,0:36:47.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you happy that I'm home?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.44,0:36:50.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.17,0:36:53.94,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.08,0:36:55.98,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.54,0:36:59.68,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Because I've been waiting this whole time, since you left this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.81,0:37:01.68,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,for you to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.82,0:37:05.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.83,0:37:16.97,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Stroke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.20,0:37:18.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.67,0:37:19.73,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Stroke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.74,0:37:23.51,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I waited like a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.21,0:38:06.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.29,0:38:15.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What a good boy, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.61,0:38:40.95,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.08,0:38:42.52,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't cross the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.52,0:38:43.45,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.75,0:38:45.45,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't have any pet-kissing fetishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.45,0:38:47.56,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Are you serious? I always did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.56,0:38:49.16,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Like to my friend's kitty. Muah muah muah muah~
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.27,0:38:52.89,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No way, not that.\NRecently there have been a lot of cases of infections by pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.89,0:38:55.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not good to indiscriminately kiss or sleep beside your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.10,0:38:56.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's what I read before in the Lifestyle column.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.80,0:38:59.43,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Infection? It's okay, I don't have any diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.43,0:39:00.64,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Well, I do have asthma, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.64,0:39:02.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And why are you talking to me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.74,0:39:05.54,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Only men who are taller than me and higher in education and income can talk to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.54,0:39:06.94,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What?! That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.94,0:39:08.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I decided it that way. How tall are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.08,0:39:13.25,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,169 cm…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.30,0:39:14.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm 172 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.75,0:39:18.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I am higher than you in height, education and income.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.10,0:39:20.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you're a pet, act like one and don't do anything unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.02,0:39:23.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.90,0:40:06.67,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Mama~
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.21,0:40:13.21,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,How is the new department?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.91,0:40:15.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.74,0:40:19.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't feel nerve-wracked trying to get in things at the last minute for midnight deadlines,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.95,0:40:22.98,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,and I don't have to worry about other papers getting breaking stories first.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.98,0:40:24.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Plus, I can have Sundays off.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.32,0:40:28.16,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You finally get some free time, and you don't know what to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.46,0:40:29.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I walk my pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.03,0:40:31.59,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Coming all the way to the suburbs like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.59,0:40:34.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because if I'm seen by any coworkers, it'll be a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.13,0:40:37.93,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,And where is he, that pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.47,0:40:49.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Aren't those shoes cute? I bought them for him in Shibuya the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.81,0:40:52.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,although I was a little annoyed that the size was the same as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.35,0:40:54.92,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,And what an agile pet he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.05,0:40:56.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He told me he does modern dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.95,0:40:58.62,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,He must be young. How old is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.62,0:40:59.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,20 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.49,0:41:02.66,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Really? Are you sure he's not a minor still?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.76,0:41:05.83,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Maybe… It doesn't matter. It's not like I'm gonna keep him for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.06,0:41:07.26,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.53,0:41:10.30,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,I thought you were totally into this new boy pet thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.90,0:41:10.93,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,Into?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.16,0:41:14.67,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No way. How would I get like that over a pet with no common sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.67,0:41:16.07,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.47,0:41:16.33,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.33,0:41:17.53,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And it's kind of irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.54,0:41:20.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,From morning to night, it's "Sumire-chan, Sumire-chan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.28,0:41:22.98,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,It's cute that he clings to you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.98,0:41:25.45,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Why don't you guys do it once before you kick him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.45,0:41:26.21,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.21,0:41:29.24,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Look at him, he's cute. And at a ripe age to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.25,0:41:32.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait, don't say such things in broad daylight in a park full of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.25,0:41:32.29,petto overlap,Yuri,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.29,0:41:33.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.02,0:41:33.92,petto overlap,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.06,0:41:37.69,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh, here he comes…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.93,0:41:39.16,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Who is the old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.93,0:41:41.73,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Who are you calling an old lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.47,0:41:46.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yuri-chan is my childhood friend. We went to middle school and high school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.80,0:41:48.50,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.50,0:41:51.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,At 23, she got married to her handsome pilot boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.49,0:41:53.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,and now she's a wealthy young wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.38,0:41:55.31,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh Sumire, you're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.81,0:41:57.11,petto overlap,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought she was just some lady from the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.98,0:42:01.65,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Yeah, actually, I think you should throw this away immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.96,0:42:12.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yuri-chan… you said he was at a ripe age…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.30,0:42:18.03,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.43,0:42:20.74,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Ran, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.74,0:42:21.57,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.57,0:42:23.55,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,We can come tomorrow. Say bye to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.00,0:42:23.70,petto overlap,girl,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.64,0:42:25.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.74,0:42:28.40,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Yeah, my mother-in-law is coming over today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.58,0:42:31.05,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Being a housewife is a task in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.05,0:42:32.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thanks for listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.28,0:42:35.32,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'm glad you weren't as down as I expected you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.39,0:42:42.66,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You should find a new man soon, instead of just some pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.92,0:42:43.99,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.06,0:42:46.36,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,See you later. Say "bye bye".
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.36,0:42:47.80,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.10,0:42:55.14,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.77,0:42:58.34,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Nevermind, let's go home. You played enough, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.34,0:42:59.84,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Already???
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.84,0:43:02.25,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,This is our first date!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.30,0:43:03.55,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I told you this is a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.31,0:43:07.12,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Man… oh, then pull me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.12,0:43:10.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? If you're not gonna follow me, I don't mind just throwing you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.35,0:43:14.16,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You're kidding! Wait for me, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.00,0:43:22.30,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Oh, it moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.30,0:43:23.03,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.57,0:43:25.93,petto,girl,0,0,0,,It's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.93,0:43:27.24,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's kicking?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.24,0:43:29.90,petto,girl,0,0,0,,I dunno, but it's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.65,0:44:16.18,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, about me…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.22,0:44:23.22,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You should've lied and said I was your new boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.22,0:44:25.29,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That' was him, right? Your ex-boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.03,0:44:27.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with you, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.26,0:44:29.10,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.30,0:44:33.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But I thought you were a lot cuter than that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.60,0:44:35.84,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You're pretty and you're good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.50,0:44:40.68,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's good that you broke up with him. He looks like a guy with no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.41,0:44:44.48,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm really happy when I'm walking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.48,0:44:47.85,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I feel cool walking with a beautiful person like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.68,0:44:52.29,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You're too good for a loser like that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.45,0:44:54.09,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I told you it has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.46,0:44:56.66,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What's with you? Don't talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.49,0:45:02.50,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sorry, I just wanted to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.60,0:45:06.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You think that's cheering me up? You've got to be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.00,0:45:08.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm not so weak as to have you cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.20,0:45:11.27,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.21,0:45:14.68,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Because I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.48,0:45:19.68,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,that you're actually very gentle and really lonely deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.45,0:45:28.66,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I was so happy I almost cried when you made me curry, and when you bought me new shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.66,0:45:30.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's just my obligation as your owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.46,0:45:32.26,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But but but…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.49,0:45:33.83,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.06,0:45:36.33,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say? You're just a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.46,0:45:38.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you're a pet, then shut up and just sit over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.50,0:45:39.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't talk like you know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.07,0:45:43.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Just because you've been with me a few days, don't try to delve into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.17,0:45:47.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't bother me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.08,0:45:52.05,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That kind of hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.05,0:45:55.02,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Be quiet, be quiet! Don't talk anymore, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.58,0:45:58.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Just get out, I'll give you money.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.46,0:46:04.43,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Get out, I like being by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.80,0:46:08.70,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.66,0:46:11.27,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Then do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.09,0:46:36.09,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.32,0:46:39.56,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,You were in the park earlier, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.33,0:46:42.76,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,With Iwaya-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.63,0:46:49.00,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, you're talking about Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.72,0:47:04.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.15,0:47:07.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, I'm sorry—
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.56,0:47:11.16,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Sorry, this is kind of sudden…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.66,0:47:14.46,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Your cousin was downstairs and let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.17,0:47:28.24,petto,,0,0,0,,Over here, Jolly!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.16,0:47:48.50,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.03,0:47:51.20,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.80,0:47:57.81,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Let's go back together. Sensei…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.81,0:47:58.81,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I won't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.34,0:48:01.88,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'm going to Germany soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.48,0:48:03.45,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.78,0:48:05.88,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yes, to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.15,0:48:07.45,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.35,0:48:13.36,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,So, tell them that I want to be left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.32,0:48:16.54,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Until then, I'll just find some random place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.69,0:48:22.73,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well, I'd found a place I could stay for two or three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.50,0:48:25.47,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,but I think I got a little too comfortable…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.47,0:48:29.04,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'll just find another place on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.58,0:48:35.84,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.41,0:48:39.85,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Oh, umm… I think I stepped on some dog poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.85,0:48:40.82,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.39,0:48:48.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.99,0:48:51.46,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.53,0:48:52.79,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I'll go home right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.00,0:48:55.80,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,It's not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.83,0:49:04.11,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I just wanted to let you know that I'm going to be transferred to the Aomori Factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.91,0:49:14.62,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you about things before I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.75,0:49:16.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't have anything to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.09,0:49:22.49,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.49,0:49:23.19,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.39,0:49:25.43,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm more surprised that you would come visit after all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.43,0:49:27.43,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't need you taking pity on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.87,0:49:37.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh and, just to let you know, that guy isn't my cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.97,0:49:40.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He's a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.31,0:49:41.04,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,A pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.04,0:49:42.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, he's my pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.91,0:49:44.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I started taking care of him after we broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.75,0:49:47.02,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.35,0:49:52.89,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,By pet, do you mean you're going out with that young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.89,0:49:55.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's not it. A pet is a pet. That's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.26,0:49:56.69,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.06,0:49:59.49,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I didn't know my cheating was that much of a shock for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.49,0:50:00.15,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.16,0:50:02.30,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Is he a host? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.40,0:50:06.30,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Because you can pay well, he's been clinging to you, is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.30,0:50:12.84,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I can't believe you'd become interested in a guy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.84,0:50:14.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe I got interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.28,0:50:16.28,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.38,0:50:18.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It was fun, this one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.01,0:50:23.69,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,What are you saying? This is no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.69,0:50:25.89,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,You should cut him off immediately.\NA guy like that who hasn't an ounce of pride…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.89,0:50:27.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, and what is pride to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.96,0:50:31.69,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't know what pride means to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.79,0:50:34.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,but a truly strong person doesn't care about stuff like pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.60,0:50:38.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You were constantly telling me back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.03,0:50:41.90,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,"You're lucky… you're pretty and smart… and get lots of salary… you're lucky, lucky…"
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.90,0:50:44.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not noticing that I was tired of that, every day…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.91,0:50:47.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And after all that, you ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.41,0:50:48.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean, pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.94,0:50:54.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That boy who has no pride at all is much better than someone who is always envying others.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.85,0:50:56.38,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,A lot better than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.49,0:51:07.43,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.03,0:51:17.27,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,You took care of that violet all this time…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.98,0:51:22.11,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,the nioi-sumire.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.85,0:51:30.65,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I thought you'd throw away everything I'd given you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.79,0:51:35.72,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I'm glad…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.53,0:51:41.06,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,that in the end, I got to hear how you really felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.77,0:51:47.74,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,When you found out about my cheating,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.50,0:51:52.91,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,you didn't lose your composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.38,0:51:59.65,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,We broke up without a fuss,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.62,0:52:07.36,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,so I always wondered in the back of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.06,0:52:11.30,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.90,0:52:17.97,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,so it was good to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.20,0:52:22.90,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.14,0:52:25.27,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.49,0:52:42.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.90,0:52:48.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Take care…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.13,0:52:54.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.64,0:52:56.64,petto,ex-boyfriend,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.76,0:53:49.89,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.20,0:53:56.60,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.87,0:53:59.90,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.67,0:54:06.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I really liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.18,0:54:12.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He was plain and boring
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.58,0:54:17.02,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,and not cool at all, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.42,0:54:24.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,he was gentle and really treated me like I was valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.64,0:54:39.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I really liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.39,0:54:55.69,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.66,0:55:01.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.65,0:55:19.08,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.55,0:55:26.22,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}as I watched her beautiful tears, that I thought I would like to stay her pet a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.62,0:55:30.00,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least until spring comes to an end.***
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.00,0:55:34.40,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least until spring comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.03,0:55:38.40,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.01,0:55:50.01,signs,text,0,0,0,,[sign]In the office
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.31,0:55:53.71,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san, Dr. Ogawa's data has come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.75,0:55:54.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.58,0:55:55.82,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Umm, if you all have time,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.82,0:55:58.19,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,why don't we all go see the cherry blossoms together?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.09,0:55:58.82,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's already this late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.82,0:56:01.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Shoot, I forgot to prepare Momo's meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.36,0:56:02.02,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.02,0:56:03.53,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but after I take this to the Imaging Center,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.53,0:56:04.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I think I'll just go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.86,0:56:06.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Please leave the papers on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.36,0:56:07.60,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.86,0:56:09.70,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I wonder what's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.70,0:56:12.30,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Oh, it seems like she recently got a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.30,0:56:14.30,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.30,0:56:16.64,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,But something changed about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.64,0:56:19.71,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Right? Right? That's what I thought too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.81,0:56:20.78,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.91,0:56:22.94,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.58,0:56:25.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.45,0:56:27.94,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,The shampoo started stinging on my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.55,0:56:28.78,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.66,0:56:30.76,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,So please, can you wash my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.79,0:56:31.99,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.44,0:56:32.69,petto overlap,Momo,0,0,0,,Please, wash my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.69,0:56:33.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.14,0:56:34.02,petto overlap,Momo,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.22,0:56:36.62,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That feels good~
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.62,0:56:38.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, hold still!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.26,0:56:40.33,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you wearing those sunglasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.33,0:56:43.06,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,Затем,Because I don't want to see you naked, it's better with these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.06,0:56:45.20,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't mind you seeing~ Here, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.30,0:56:47.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Even if you don't mind, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.24,0:56:49.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, they're kind of clouding up…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.04,0:56:52.01,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Huh? Ouch! Your finger went into my eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.81,0:56:54.01,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.51,0:56:58.00,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,There's tears coming… Hurry up and wash it out, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.09,0:56:59.19,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.85,0:57:00.92,petto overlap,Momo,0,0,0,,Hurry, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.92,0:57:02.22,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.22,0:57:04.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two weeks since that rainy day,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.32,0:57:10.33,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.00,0:57:16.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,This story was scheduled to run for a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.33,0:57:18.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,but my chief says he wants to extend it to half a year…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.07,0:57:21.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, oh, thank you from us as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.44,0:57:24.31,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll call you again later on.\NThank you, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.11,0:57:26.94,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Why hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.04,0:57:29.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Kokeshi doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.70,0:57:39.50,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,From this week on, I have been asked to take control of the counseling room at this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.86,0:57:45.56,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I will be on the 14th floor two days a week. Please come visit sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.20,0:57:52.43,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,My Mary-chan seems to be interested in you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.64,0:58:31.24,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Wait a second…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.93,0:59:03.47,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I wonder if Sumire-chan will come home early?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.77,0:59:06.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.04,0:59:09.18,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You're Iwaya, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.71,0:59:13.35,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Long time, no see…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.72,0:59:15.55,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's been about four years, hasn't it?
